#+TITLE: Running CI tests like production
#+LANGUAGE: en
#+PROPERTY: header-args:bash :tangle no :results verbatim :cache yes 

I got burned last month: my tests passed in CI but the app crashed in
production because of a file permission bug. The tests ran as root,
but production runs as a regular user. I want my CI containers to use
the same non-root user as production so I catch these issues early.

First I set up my Dagger project and install daggerlib:

#+begin_src bash :eval no-export
dagger init --sdk=python
dagger install github.com/Konubinix/daggerlib
#+end_src

The following is only for testing purposes — it makes the project
use the local daggerlib checkout instead of the published version:

#+begin_src bash :eval no-export
sed -i '/pin/d; s|"github.com/Konubinix/daggerlib@main"|"../.."|; s|"\.\./\.\.",|"../.."|' dagger.json
#+end_src

#+RESULTS[5b6339ed6b209c2bc103c0b4e60ac9dd71b8e70a]:


Then I write my Dagger module. Each =<<...>>= reference is defined in
the sections below — they show the function code and its output:

#+begin_src python :tangle .dagger/src/non_root_user/main.py :noweb yes
import dagger
from dagger import dag, function, object_type


@object_type
class NonRootUser:
    <<whoami-check>>
    <<home-check>>
    <<uid-check>>
    <<debian-uid-check>>
#+end_src

* Making sure the test container runs as a regular user

  First I need to verify that my test container actually runs as a
  non-root user, not root:

  #+NAME: alpine_user_whoami
  #+begin_src fixtureyaml :eval no-export
userfunction: whoami-check
project: examples/non_root_user
func: alpine-user
chain:
  - with-exec: [whoami]
  - stdout
  #+end_src

#+RESULTS: alpine_user_whoami
:results:
#+NAME: whoami-check
#+begin_src python
@function
async def whoami_check(self) -> str:
    """Generated from test spec."""
    return await (
        dag.lib().alpine_user()
        .with_exec(['whoami'])
        .stdout()
    )
#+end_src

#+NAME: alpine_user_whoami-run
#+begin_src bash
dagger call whoami-check
#+end_src

#+RESULTS[8d63cd1e2dfadbd202a15c00ec187ca92f4065a4]: alpine_user_whoami-run

#+BEGIN_SRC org :tangle (expand-file-name "tests/expected/alpine_user_whoami" (locate-dominating-file default-directory ".git")) :noweb yes :exports none :comments no :padline no
<<alpine_user_whoami-run()>>
#+END_SRC
:end:
