* Matching the production UID

  Our Kubernetes pods run with UID 1000. I need the CI user to have
  the same UID so that volume mounts and file ownership behave
  identically:

  #+NAME: alpine_user_id
  #+begin_src fixtureyaml :eval no-export
userfunction: uid-check
project: examples/non_root_user
func: alpine-user
chain:
  - with-exec: ["id", sam]
  - stdout
  #+end_src

